Python based script to talk to a polargraph and graph the results of a twitter search.

Requires pySerial and TwitterSearch (get them by running "pip install pyserial" and "pip install TwitterSearch")

Also requires a twitter API key. You will need to setup a twitter dev account to get a key.

Script should run with Python 2.7 & 3.x

To use, edit machine specif config values in pylargraph.py then run pylargraph.py and follow the on screen instructions.
